SignServer TimeMonitor 3.6.0, 2014
----------------------------------

Beginning with SignServer 3.6, the TimeMonitor will be included in the
SignServer (EE) releases.

See the SignServer ChangeLog instead.


SignServer TimeMonitor 1.1.5, 2013-09-19
----------------------------------------

 * Fixes TimeMonitor leaving TCP connections in state CLOSE_WAIT


SignServer TimeMonitor 1.1.4, 2013-09-16
----------------------------------------

 * Fixes TimeMonitor leaking file descriptors
 * Fixes HTTP error response from server flooding log


SignServer TimeMonitor 1.1.3, 2013-09-05
----------------------------------------

 * Fixes TimeMonitor not treating stratum 0 as error
 * Fixes Unknown leap code error flooding log 


SignServer TimeMonitor 1.1.2, 2013-05-14
----------------------------------------

 * Added ability to set multiple NTP servers in TimeMonitor 	


SignServer TimeMonitor 1.1.1, 2013-04-25
----------------------------------------

 * TimeMonitor now logs "back in calibration" at INFO level instead of ERROR


SignServer TimeMonitor 1.1.0, 2013-01-04
----------------------------------------

 * Leap second support in SignServer TimeMonitor


SignServer TimeMonitor 1.0.0, 2012-12-28
----------------------------------------

* Initial version. 

